From: Minime <maintainers@minime-os.local>
Date: Wed, 09 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] package/u-boot: add hash for u-boot 2026.07

u-boot 2026.07 was released 2026-07-07 and post-dates Buildroot
2026.02.3. Add its SHA256 so BR2_TARGET_UBOOT_CUSTOM_VERSION_VALUE
="2026.07" passes hash verification.

SHA256 computed from https://ftp.denx.de/pub/u-boot/u-boot-2026.07.tar.bz2

Signed-off-by: Minime <maintainers@minime-os.local>
---
 package/u-boot/u-boot.hash | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/package/u-boot/u-boot.hash b/package/u-boot/u-boot.hash
index 1111111..2222222 100644
--- a/package/u-boot/u-boot.hash
+++ b/package/u-boot/u-boot.hash
@@ -1,3 +1,4 @@
 # Locally computed
+sha256  78e8bfc382fe388f9b55aa1daf8c563522a037779b5d4c349d1415e381f1243e  u-boot-2026.07.tar.bz2
